      <div class="section-card">
        <div class="section-head">
          <div><div class="section-kicker">Document Gaps</div><div class="section-title">What will slow the family down</div><div class="section-copy">Missing documents do not just create legal risk. They create Monday-morning bottlenecks when bills, accounts, and medical records need attention.</div></div>
          <div class="pill" id="gapPill">Readiness gaps</div>
        </div>
        <div class="action-grid">
          <div class="action-card"><div class="action-label">Gap One</div><div class="metric-value" id="gapOneTitle">—</div><div class="action-copy" id="gapOneCopy">—</div></div>
          <div class="action-card"><div class="action-label">Gap Two</div><div class="metric-value" id="gapTwoTitle">—</div><div class="action-copy" id="gapTwoCopy">—</div></div>
          <div class="action-card"><div class="action-label">Gap Three</div><div class="metric-value" id="gapThreeTitle">—</div><div class="action-copy" id="gapThreeCopy">—</div></div>
